channel.title: ::vote command [delta]
channel.description:
i saw the tutorial for vote commands for pi, so i tought id try to convert them to delta but all i got was errors :o
so, i need an idea of how the commands should look like.
1. ::vote for players to enter and the votepage will pop up 2. ::voteall for owner(s) that will open up the votepage for all online players
